{"tid":1784181,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"疑似藍屍扮黑警手持行山杖同木棍 恐嚇記者？","createTime":"2019-12-15T13:10:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-15T13:58:09.000Z","uid":222970,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"d29eafb5d1835c8d1cbe0b0c7fec1dc8e1cd3541","tid":1784181,"uid":222970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-15T13:10:40.000Z","msg":"【15/12 沙田和你shop】<br />\n<br />\n新城市廣場發現數名形跡可疑的男子，當中有人手持武器，包括行山杖、木棍等，有市民質疑為便衣警察。記者尾隨追問，幾名男子便揮動武器並指向記者，最後登上的士離開。<br />\n<br />\n#非法藏有攻擊性武器<br />\n<br />\n攝：鄧家烜<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>認真，有冇人知佢地咩人？論枝棍 身形 長髮 又唔似便衣狗，更加唔係自己手足，但可以肯定係中坑黎，各位小心唔知佢地有咩企圖，可能係藍屍假扮示威者刻意向記者同平民攻擊，用黎抺黑醜化抗爭者！</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0kN9ra6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0kN9ra6.jpg&h=67211e5e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/edXmhhN.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FedXmhhN.jpg&h=2b21a57e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/n9zG1Kt.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fn9zG1Kt.jpg&h=50f607f9&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3eef34b011e8465921ccb6c6d44dfd9eaac33155","tid":1784181,"uid":202524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-15T13:11:45.000Z","msg":"唔好意思 借個位黎<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: green;\">德國戰線要人</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n冇時間啦25號截止，極度要人幫手!<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1782422\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1782422</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"c06ed5ecc3b45a8f08e910aac512f7424b4379c7","tid":1784181,"uid":222970,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-15T13:13:35.000Z","msg":"恐嚇記者一定唔係同路人！！！佢地一定係想假扮示威者行平民攻擊 偽旗行動"},{"pid":"f991b447b9234fcdf66dc4ca302edb2635584329","tid":1784181,"uid":189328,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019